* '''Grok''' is used mainly by the [[geek]] [[subculture]], though it was heavily used by the [[counterculture]] of the 1960s, as evidenced by its repeated appearance in Tom Wolfe's “{{w|The Electric Kool-Aid Acid Test}}.”

